description: Louie B. Fresh Mobile Kitchen and Catering serves up the freshest, tastiest wraps and salads in Chicago! A family-run truck is a truck that you know is gonna have the best, most unique recipes, and L.B. Fresh is no exception. If you're out and about in the 'burbs, keep a weather eye out for the big blue truck and make sure to try the strawberry salad!
name: Louie B. Fresh Mobile Kitchen & Catering
